inoremap ( ()<left>
inoremap [ []<left>
inoremap " ""<left>
inoremap ' ''<left>
autocmd FileType sh 	inoremap <buffer>  ` ``<left>
autocmd FileType sh 	vnoremap <buffer>  <leader>` di`<esc>pa`<esc>
autocmd FileType vim 	inoremap <buffer>  < <><left>
